  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multi-center, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study, to assess the
      efficacy and safety of AXS-05 in the treatment of agitation in patients with Alzheimer's
      disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
